history.text: Pretty fun movie. Was this his next one after Titanic?
For Leonardo DiCaprio, I mean.
Oh I'm not sure. This movie was quite interesting.
Seems like a smart guy to begin with
Do you remember the scene where he's a doctor in this movie? My girlfriend and I ask each about concurrence all the time. Do you concur? I concur.
Yes I do.
Do you agree with the critical reception? I thought it was a standout movie for that year.
I do agree, in fact it is one of my all time favorite movie for that year especially!
What do you think about the last critical response on the list? I can't remember if that was true or not.
I honestly, was far too young at the time to remember such a hype, however I do think it's a bit of an exaggeration
From one to ten, ten being the best of all. How would you rate this movie personally?
I would rate it a seven. You?
Is this your favorite genre of movie?
Probably an 8 because it's one of my favorite movies. Do you remember at the beginning of the movie when Frank impersonated as a French Teacher?
It isn't actually, but the plot of this movie made it one of my most faves!
What would you rate it, from 1 to 10?
an eight (:
Do you think Leonardo DiCaprio did a really great job at the beginning of the movie when he was a French Teacher?
Tell me what you think.
I really enjoyed that scene.
I liked that it was based on a true story. What did you think of the person the film is based on?
I think he's quite smart for the actions he's done throughout the whole storyline.
Real Frank?
Yes.
Quick question off the topic, because I'm really impressed. Are you AI, or a real person?
I don't know who AI is.... I'm pretty sure I'm a real person though.
Just what an AI would say... What do you think about the latest paragraph. pretty crazy with the real guy, huh?
Which actor or actress was your favorite?
I think it's pretty good, I don't actually think that was what happened to that person that they were basing on.
Actors/Actress in the movie or ...?
yes
Leonardo DiCaprio, sounds mainstream but i really like his acting work. What about you?
Hanks and Walken, obviously
I've never watched a movie from neither of them besides this movie..
Surely you can't be serious
I am serious.
I think we're good to go now. Goodbye, possibly robot person!
Have a nice night!

uid1response.feedback: The other user was rather not fully focussed on the discussion, and at times I thought he did not think read what my response was.

uid2response.feedback: If this is an AI generated script, I was very impressed. Seemed like it passed on context clues and maybe previous answers, but told me it had only seen tom hanks and christoper walken in this single movie, which is basically a huge tell.
